name: A Year in Portraits by Jeremy Cowart

metadata.name: 2022 A Year in Portraits - #0001
metadata.description: A Year in Portraits is a collaboration between photographer Jeremy Cowart and Larkhaus. We invite you to experience an interactive digital publication featuring a series of portraits and insights from the leading voices in Web3 photographed in Jeremy's distinctive style at major Web3 events in 2022. The 2022 Edition marks the beginning of this project that we hope to continue to create for many years as the Web3 space continues to grow and develop.
